            <div type="transcript" id="J1239">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Risk is the Hair that holds the Tun</l>
                    <l>Seductive in the Air --</l>
                    <l>That <app type="revision"><lem>one</lem><rdg>one</rdg></app>
Tun is hollow -- but the Tun --</l>
                    <l>With Hundred Weights -- to spare --</l>
                    <l>Too ponderous to suspect the snare</l>
                    <l>Espies that fickle chair</l>
                    <l>And seats itself to be let go</l>
                    <l>By that perfidious Hair --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The "foolish Tun" the Critics say --</l>
                    <l>While that <app type="revision"><lem>obliging --</lem><rdg>obliging --</rdg></app>
<app type="revision"><lem>enchanting</lem><rdg>enchanting</rdg></app>
delusive Hair</l>
                    <l>Persuasive as Perdition,</l>
                    <l>Decoys it's <app type="revision"><lem>Passenger</lem><rdg>Passenger</rdg></app>
Traveller</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                </lg>
